parameters:
Dining Hall Chef: If you have the skills to handle such
lively prey, would you mind helping me out?

Dining Hall Chef: I guess I have no choice... Shall I ask
the warriors of the Bulk Brigade?

Dining Hall Chef: That would be a great help! I'll guide you
to the kitchen!

Dining Hall Chef: You seem like warriors from the Bulk
Brigade! Please accept my gratitude for your cooperation.

Dining Hall Chef: Hey, hey, are you guys okay? It would be a
big problem if you became ingredients.

events.name: お料理バトル吹き出し

parameters:
Warrior of the Bulk Brigade: A hungry stomach cannot fight.
Eating is also a training to become a better warrior.

Cafeteria Staff: Just between you and me, I like
intellectual people, but in this place... hmm, my chances
are slim.

Lumberjack Man: After work, there's nothing like a cold beer
at the dining hall!

Warrior of the Flow: This place has a tense atmosphere. If
you call yourself a warrior... there are many who draw their
swords, you know.

Dining Hall Lady: We have plenty of energizing dishes! We
have fresh meat and delicious cheese, you know!

Female Beer Craftsman: Women who support warriors are also
important. We must eat as much as we can and then return to
work.

events.name: QI｢イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼｣
EV011イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼1-5

parameters:
It's you guys from the Bulk Gang! How about trying Valto's
cooking?
Thief Nora: Really, is it okay!?

Priestess Sophia: Today, I have come as a messenger of the
shrine maiden.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Our message has arrived...! Forget
about the meal, I want you to come to my house right away.
Thief Nora: H-Hey, is it not allowed to have a meal!?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: EV013イミセリノスの巫女からの依頼1-6

parameters:
Goat of the Bulk Gang: 'We have a very important matter that
we would like to apologize for.'

Priestess Sophia: We have come as messengers of the
priestess of Imiserinos.
Goat of the Bulk Gang: ...What did you just say?

Priestess Sophia: We are messengers of the priestess of
Imiserinos--

Goat of the Bulk Gang: You're not the priestess of Actina,
are you!?

Goat of the Bulk Gang: So you're not the priestess of
Actina... Are you really here as messengers of the priestess
of Imiserinos?

Priestess Sophia: Yes, we are messengers of the priestess of
Imiserinos.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: I see, so the goddess Actina has
abandoned me.

Priestess Sophia: A story about a close friend transforming
into an ogre... I felt that there was something
intentionally hidden.

Priestess Sophia: If you could tell us the story, there
might be something we can help with.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: Let me tell you everything... about
the curse that has long plagued the Bulk Gang.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: In the Bulk Gang, occasionally there
are individuals who transform into ogres, and each time,
someone close to them is tasked with subduing them.
Clea: The ones we defeated too...

Goat of the Bulk Gang: He is also a victim of the curse, and
I myself have also begun to be consumed by the curse.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: There are priests and mages who want
to break the curse that plagues the Bulk Gang. They want to
request assistance to find a solution.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: It's impossible for me to solve this
on my own...!

Priestess Sophia: Of course, it is also a request from the
priestess of Imiserinos.

Mage Relm: The Bulk Gang should have little to do with
magic... There must be something special influencing them...

Goat of the Bulk Gang: If it becomes impossible to resolve
the situation with warriors and thieves, I want you to
subdue the [monsters].

Goat of the Bulk Gang: It's not that I don't trust my
comrades, but I can trust you since you defeated the dragon.

Clea: I will definitely find a way to prevent that from
happening.

Goat of the Bulk Gang: There isn't much time left. The curse
is definitely reaching my soul.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
